# âš¡ Interview One-liner

> ViewBag and ViewData are used to pass data from controller to view for a single request, while TempData is used to persist data across requests mainly during redirects.

---

# âœ… Key Notes

* Prefer Model over all 3
* TempData is auto-cleared after read
* ViewBag internally uses ViewData

